{"tid":1159040,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］點解鬼佬食用魚既種類咁少","createTime":"2019-05-17T11:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T12:56:01.000Z","uid":247651,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"734c857ea3ae0b84920e76ef317ba7ce45257431","tid":1159040,"uid":247651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"呢排重睇HELL'S KITCHEN 發覺鬼佬（歐洲，北美）既食用魚<br />\n黎黎去去都係SALMON, TUNA, SEABASS, CATFISH 等等　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再高級D就TURBOT （之後就數唔出）<br />\n<br />\n比較返亞洲種類好多,淡水去到鹹水都有<br />\n例如香港有 倉魚,桂花,馬頭,紅杉,九棍,OOXX斑 等等　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本都有 鰈魚,鯖魚,香魚,鰤魚 等等　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底係以前漁業發展既問題，定係飲食文化既影響，定抑或係小弟孤陋寡聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求高手賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c1d82cb794f18a39e70df3d3ae1cb5ee8197a7","tid":1159040,"uid":31108,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"應該關佢地既煮食方式事掛<br />\n佢地煮魚多數炸,烤,燒,焗<br />\n用依啲方法煮既魚要多肉少骨先得<br />\n而且亞洲魚(特別係淡水魚)好多都要醃菜煮先好食<br />\n好似冬菜 雪菜咁<br />\n鬼佬識鬼咁食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4210fee79e9e2ac0ffd08c437f5a97b15281f83c","tid":1159040,"uid":247651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c1d82cb794f18a39e70df3d3ae1cb5ee8197a7","tid":1159040,"uid":31108,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:45:51.000Z","msg":"應該關佢地既煮食方式事掛<br />\n佢地煮魚多數炸,烤,燒,焗<br />\n用依啲方法煮既魚要多肉少骨先得<br />\n而且亞洲魚(特別係淡水魚)好多都要醃菜煮先好食<br />\n好似冬菜 雪菜咁<br />\n鬼佬識鬼咁食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得純粹因為魚既腥味而唔食既可能性比較低<br />\n歐美個邊咁多香料，調味粉，而且係煮法上黎講<br />\n煎炸焗烤　好多時候都會比起　蒸煮　更加僻腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef5be4be913cdd555ab6a6b42ca75130ef3e588","tid":1159040,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼佬不嬲食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"92d629147f14de3c602cb8b3497ee8de9c4e80e9","tid":1159040,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"唔係少，但因為你熟悉亞洲多過「鬼佬」咪咁覺得<br />\n靠山食山靠水食水，唔會因爲咩人種所以少啲"},{"pid":"584abf51ad25c336b577fdb7668c3dec4fc97eee","tid":1159040,"uid":31414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"Fish and chips都大把白肉魚簡啦"},{"pid":"094fa819f73de56c468ac4e502720e1830f86bef","tid":1159040,"uid":225371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"歐洲有人食七鰓鰻，仲要被視為美食。"},{"pid":"ff5d41b3c68da4e425c13f9085f16f4219355216","tid":1159040,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"因為大部份鬼佬都唔鐘意食魚"}]}